  "text": "From our results we get, relying on Bourgain [CITATION_1] , the following corollary. Corollary 1.3 Let G be given as in Theorem 1.1 or 1.2. Then G has a quasiisometrically embedded tree, and in particular G does not quasi-isometrically embed into any uniformly convex (or superreflexive) Banach space.",
